# GitHub API Token for creating issues from user feedback
# How to create:
# 1. Go to https://github.com/settings/tokens?type=beta (Fine-grained tokens)
# 2. Click "Generate new token"
# 3. Name: "ChurchHub Feedback Bot" (or similar)
# 4. Expiration: Choose as needed (recommend 1 year or no expiration)
# 5. Repository access: Select "Only select repositories" -> radio-crestin/church-hub
# 6. Permissions -> Repository permissions -> Issues: Read and Write
# 7. Click "Generate token" and copy the value
GITHUB_TOKEN=github_pat_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
